PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food of ELEANOR M. HART, of Woodstock, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Farm Credit Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, in the place of George Klosler, whose term has expired.
